s. a corn measure as படி ex pressed by being the eigth part of a குறுணி or marcal
ஒருநாழி
இருநாழி
c.
one measure; two measures c.
to eight which is a marcal
2. [corrup. from sa. nadi.]
tubularity
any thing tubular
உட்டுளைப்பொருள்
